cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep learning network for action recognition using SPD matrices. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also involves the development of novel layers, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves the use of deep learning for classification, which can be categorized under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
